title: Collin Raye Performs His Biggest 90’s Hits + Bobby’s Top 5 Jake Owen Birthday Songs + Arkansas Keith Solves Bobby’s Antler Debate
itunes:title: Collin Raye Performs His Biggest 90’s Hits + Bobby’s Top 5 Jake Owen Birthday Songs + Arkansas Keith Solves Bobby’s Antler Debate
description:
Collin Raye stops by and performs his biggest hits from the 90’s including Little Rock, That’s My Story and more! Bobby pays tribute to Jake Owen on his 39th Birthday with his Top 5 Favorite songs. Plus, Bobby’s former stepdad Arkansas Keith calls in to weigh in on Eddie’s pink tricycle situation and solves the antler debate!
